Finland Bank tender rate unchanged at 3 . 00 pct . The Bank of Finland drained 8 . 12 billion markka ( $ 1 . 5 billion ) of spot liquidity on Tuesday in an auction of one - month paper at an unchanged 3 . 00 percent tender rate SPFH . Before the opening , the central bank forecast a spot liquidity surplus of 12 . 90 billion markka . The required daily balance for banks was 7 . 31 billion markka . The Bank of Finland ' s tender rate , or chief monetary policy tool , has been unchanged since it was lowered to 3 . 00 percent from 3 . 10 percent on October 9 , 1996 . - - Helsinki newsroom + 358 - 9 - 6805 0245 , news @ reuters . fi ( $ = 5 . 496 Finnish Markka ) 
